* This file contains the command line arguments for cgmp when running in parallel
*
* mpirun -np 1 -all-local ../bin/cgmp
*
* mpirun -np 2 -all-local tobp
* mpirun -np 2 -all-local -gdb tobp
* 
* mpirun -np 1 -all-local --dbg=valgrindebug tobp
* mpirun -np 2 -all-local -dbg=valgrindebug tobp
* mpirun -np 2 -machinefile machinefile tobp
*
* mpirun -tv -np 2 -all-local tobp
* mpirun -tv -np 2 -all-local tobp
* mpirun -np 1 -all-local tobp
* mcr:
* mpirun-wdh -np 1 tobp
* mpirun-wdh -np 2 tobp
* mcr:
*   totalview srun -a -N2 -n2 -ppdebug tobp
*
* mpirun-wdh -np 2 -ppdebug tob
*
* ============= multi-physics ==================
*
* noplot ins/p.cmd
